headline: CrowdStrike Named an Inaugural Google Unified Security Recommended Partner
summary: AUSTIN, Texas, November 13, 2025--CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) today announced that it was named one of three inaugural partners in the Google Unified Security Recommended program, recognizing the AI-native CrowdStrike Falcon® platform for endpoint protection. CrowdStrike is the only inaugural endpoint technology selected by Google for the Unified Security Recommended program.
